erl/ean-search.pl?ean=3D9000000000000&amp;page=3D1">9...</a>
</p><p>

</p><p>
</p><div itemscope=3D"" itemprop=3D"mainEntity" itemtype=3D"https://schema.=
org/Question">
<h2 itemprop=3D"name">Is there an API to query the EAN database?</h2>
<div itemscope=3D"" itemprop=3D"acceptedAnswer" itemtype=3D"https://schema.=
org/Answer"><div itemprop=3D"text">
For all automated queries, please use oue <a href=3D"https://www.ean-search=
.org/ean-database-api.html" target=3D"_top">barcode API</a>. You can use th=
e API to integrate our database into your own applications. (<a href=3D"htt=
ps://www.ean-search.org/ean-api-intro.html">some barcode API examples</a>)
</div></div></div>
<p>
</p><div itemscope=3D"" itemprop=3D"mainEntity" itemtype=3D"https://schema.=
org/Question">
<h2 itemprop=3D"name">How can I make more searches per day?</h2>
<div itemscope=3D"" itemprop=3D"acceptedAnswer" itemtype=3D"https://schema.=
org/Answer"><div itemprop=3D"text">
Due to the enormous amount of bots and scrapers, we have to limit the numbe=
rs of searches users can make on this website.
To make more searches, you have to sign up for an <a href=3D"https://www.ea=
n-search.org/ean-database-api.html" target=3D"_top">account</a>.
</div></div></div>
<p>
</p><div itemscope=3D"" itemprop=3D"mainEntity" itemtype=3D"https://schema.=
org/Question">
<h2 itemprop=3D"name"><span style=3D"color:red;">New:</span> I'm no program=
mer, how can I do bulk EAN lookups?</h2>
<div itemscope=3D"" itemprop=3D"acceptedAnswer" itemtype=3D"https://schema.=
org/Answer"><div itemprop=3D"text">
Get an <a href=3D"https://www.ean-search.org/ean-database-api.html" target=
=3D"_top">account</a> and use our <b>Excel assistant</b> to upload a list o=
f EAN codes and download the lookup results instead of doing <a href=3D"htt=
ps://www.ean-search.org/upc-barcode-lookup.html">barcode lookups</a> manual=
ly.
</div></div></div>
<p>
</p><div itemscope=3D"" itemprop=3D"mainEntity" itemtype=3D"https://schema.=
org/Question">
<h2 itemprop=3D"name">Can I use a barcode scanner?</h2>
<div itemscope=3D"" itemprop=3D"acceptedAnswer" itemtype=3D"https://schema.=
org/Answer"><div itemprop=3D"text">
Yes, you can use a professional barcode scanner and feed us the scanned bar=
codes through the API or in an Excel sheet to look up the products in our d=
atabase.
You can also use your smartphone or webcam to <a href=3D"https://www.ean-se=
arch.org/barcode-scanner.html" target=3D"_top">scan barcodes online</a>. On=
 Linux, you can use <a href=3D"https://github.com/eansearch/zbar" target=3D=
"_blank">zbarcam-qt</a> or <a href=3D"https://github.com/eansearch/BarcodeS=
canner" target=3D"_blank">BarcodeScanner</a> to scan and look up barcodes.
</div></div></div>
<p>
</p><div itemscope=3D"" itemprop=3D"mainEntity" itemtype=3D"https://schema.=
org/Question">
<h2 itemprop=3D"name">Can I download the full EAN database?</h2>
<div itemscope=3D"" itemprop=3D"acceptedAnswer" itemtype=3D"https://schema.=
org/Answer"><div itemprop=3D"text">
When you get an <a href=3D"https://www.ean-search.org/ean-database-api.html=
" target=3D"_top">account</a> you can select which part of the database you=
 want to download. Please refrain from automatic crawling of the public web=
site. Access will be blocked completely for excessive usage.
</div></div></div>
<p>
</p><div itemscope=3D"" itemprop=3D"mainEntity" itemtype=3D"https://schema.=
org/Question">
<h2 itemprop=3D"name">Is an ISBN number also a valid EAN code?</h2>
<div itemscope=3D"" itemprop=3D"acceptedAnswer" itemtype=3D"https://schema.=
org/Answer"><div itemprop=3D"text">
You can convert 10-digit ISBN numbers (ISBN-10) into ISBN-13 numbers. The I=
SBN-13 numbers are valid EAN codes and are located in "bookland" with the p=
refixes 978 and 979.=20
Our <a href=3D"https://www.ean-search.org/isbn-search.html">ISBN search</a>=
 automatically does the conversion and shows both versions.
</div></div></div>
<p>
</p><div itemscope=3D"" itemprop=3D"mainEntity" itemtype=3D"https://schema.=
org/Question">
<h2 itemprop=3D"name">How can I submit EAN codes?</h2>
<div itemscope=3D"" itemprop=3D"acceptedAnswer" itemtype=3D"https://schema.=
org/Answer"><div itemprop=3D"text">
You can <a href=3D"https://www.ean-search.org/upload.html">submit barcodes<=
/a> that are missing in our database for free (manually or as Excel sheet).
</div></div></div>
<p>
</p></div>
<h2>EAN Website Widgets</h2>
Here are some <a href=3D"https://www.ean-search.org/ean-tools.html" target=
=3D"_top">EAN widgets</a> that you can place on your own website.
<p>
</p><h2>Can I buy EAN codes from you?</h2>
We do not sell any EAN codes, but you can get them from GS1 or a reseller, =
like
